title: Tibia 8.11: Blackd Tibia Ping v1.2
description:
Blackd Tibia Ping can check how much ping you have in your world. The ping means how much delay you get between your order and the server answer You can also discover what is the best server for you if you are new in Tibia, or if you are planning to change server because you have too much lag on your current server. 


This tool was not created by me, all credits go to Blackd Tools.
